name: Interactive Multi-Game Demo Disc: Version 19
overview: Playable demos: Paper Mario: The Thousand-Year Door, Mario Power Tennis, Metroid Prime 2: Echoes, Viewtiful Joe 2, Baten Kaitos: Eternal Wings and the Lost Ocean, Mario Party 6, and Tak 2: The Staff of Dreams. In addition to the playables, the disc also features movies of: Donkey Konga, Metroid Prime 2: Echoes, Tony Hawk's Underground 2, GoldenEye: Rogue Agent, X-Men Legends, Need for Speed: Underground 2, Mario Power Tennis, The Urbz: Sims in the City, Nintendo DS, and F-Zero GP Legend (Cartoon).
